                    <msContents>
                        <summary/>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6851Prayer">Prayer against the sufferings provoked by the Budā, containing
          ʾasmāt</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስሙ፡ ለእግዚአብሔር፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ታኦስ፡ አዝዮስ፡ ማሲ፡ ማስያስ፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5888AsmatPrayer">Prayer against bāryā, Satan, and devils</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ድርሱ፡ በስመ፡ አልፋ፡ ፃዕ፡ ፃዕ፡ ፃዕ፡ ወወጺአከ፡ ኢትግባእ፡ ይቤለከ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> አንተ፡ ቡዳ፡ 
                                ወአንተ፡ ባርያ፡ ወአንተ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ወአንተ፡ ጋኔን፡ ዘትትሜሰሉ፡ በብዙኅ፡ ጾታ፡ አህያ፡ ሺራህያ፡ ይመራኤል፡ ሀያል፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5696MagicPrayer">Rampart of the Cross (General record)</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="ellipsis"/>አአምን፡ በአብ፡ አአምን፡ በወልድ፡ አአምን፡ በመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ከልለኒ፡ በወልታ፡ ርድአኒ፡ ወህፅረኒ፡ 
                                በሐፁረ፡ መስቀልከ፡ <sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ኦአምላኪያ፡</sic> <sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ወመድኀንየ፡</sic> መሐረኒ፡ 
                                ወተሠሃለኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7049Aqweyasat">ʾAnta Bāryā ṣallim gānen hǝśśum</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ብረር፡ ወከመ፡ ሰምዕ፡ ተመኃው፡ ይቤሉከ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አንተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡
                                ወመላኪሆሙ፡ ለአቍያጻት፡ አንተ፡ ባርያ፡ ጸሊም፡ ጋኔን፡ ህሡም፡ ኢትልክኑ፡ ነፍሱ፡ ወሥጋሁ፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ </incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4620Prayer">Ṣalot baʾǝnta ḥǝmāma nahabt wa-ʾagānǝnt ʾAlāhumā
          Wayānurā</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ነሀብት፡ እማሁማ፡ ወያኑራሃሸም፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                አድኅኖ፡ እምነሀብት፡ ለገብረ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ </incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7046PrayerColic">Prayer against colic</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቍርፀት፡ እንዘ፡ ይትዋነይ፡ በውስተ፡ ማኅፀን፡ እንዘ፡ ይበጽብጽ፡ ከርሠ፡
                                <sic resp="PRS8999Strelcyn">ወይፈቅል፡</sic> ቍልፈተ፡ ወይደጕጽ፡ ገበዋተ፡ ዝንቱ፡ ህማመ፡ ቍርፀት፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7042PrayerMichael">LIT7042PrayerMichael</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሌጌዎን፡ ርኩስ፡ ዘይሰልብ፡ ልበ፡ ሰብእ፡ ወያጸልም፡ አእይንተ፡ ወይመጽእ፡
                                ከመ፡ ጽላሎት፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i8">
                            <title ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT6989PPFear">Prayer against nocturnal terror</title>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ጸሎተ፡ ድንጋፄ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ባርከኒ፡ ወአድኅነኒ፡ እምድንጋፄ፡ ወእምፍርሃተ፡ ለሊት፡</incipit>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                        </msItem>
                    </msContents>
                    
